verbose_text: To further verify that the changes in cell morphology were caused by MET, we performed western blot analysis to detect the expression of epithelial marker, E-cadherin, and mesenchymal marker, vimentin, in the SCC25 cells transfected with pre-miR-485-5p and the cells transfected with control miR.
evidence: expression of epithelial marker, E-cadherin, and mesenchymal marker, vimentin
